The Melanin Lizard is a Greed Island monster that lives in the hills.

It is a large lizard that can swallow a whole cow. It can use its huge body to pin down and kill its victim by suffocation. This lizard has a mole on its back that is very vulnerable to attacks that is hidden by many other spots used as camouflage. It is claimed that it is not hard to observe which spot the lizard guards carefully.

A rank E card with a 100-card limit and a designated number of 697.
